## [CRITICAL] Version Constraints — DO NOT MODIFY
- PHP: 8.4.18 (FORBIDDEN: upgrade to 8.5+)
- Laravel: 11.51.0 (FORBIDDEN: major update)
- Filament: 3.3.49 (FORBIDDEN: v4 API or Schema patterns)
- composer.json: NEVER change versions without explicit user approval
- Sail runtime path: ./vendor/laravel/sail/runtimes/8.4 (fixed, do not alter)
- compose.yaml: preserve structure and indentation exactly

## [RULE] Filament v3 Frontend
- USE: x-filament::* and x-filament-tables::* official Blade components
- FORBIDDEN: custom <div>/<table> layouts, inline styles, <style> tags
- CSS: Tailwind utility classes only
- DO NOT break Filament-generated class structures (fi-section, fi-input-wrp, etc.)

## [RULE] Compact UI
- Reduce default spacing by one step (e.g. gap-y-4 → gap-y-2)
- Remove empty fi-section-header via header(null)
- Prefer table layout over card layout for list views
- Use grid for horizontal input layout; avoid tall vertical pages
- Responsive grid: grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3

## [RULE] Robustness
- Live inputs: wire:model.live.debounce.500ms required
- Numeric inputs: numeric + step="0.001"
- Images/large elements: aspect-video + overflow-hidden
- On layout issues: replace custom implementation with standard Filament components first